{
  "stem": "27390.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we could hear-- they told us that the Germans had broken through the front line and they are-- and the Poles are retreating but we're not to tell anybody about it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in the meantime, the radio was blaring away the victories, what they have achieved.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It was in complete contradiction to what was going on on the ground.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was about 11 o'clock at night and after the air raid was over, we went into our apartment and we laid down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We've didn't undress but we laid down to have a few hours sleep.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "About 2 o'clock in the morning, there was a bang on the door, on our door and one of my uncles came in, and he said, get up, quick.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everybody's running away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Germans are coming in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took everybody-- before the war broke out, everybody prepared themselves a rucksack with some main provisions, a bit of food and some clothes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But us children, we had a-- a bit of money on our-- in a little bag and a label on the-- with the name, the address and everything.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we put that on quickly and we run out into the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we came into the street, already there were thousands and thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the streets were packed and everybody was running.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody knew where they're running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was chaos.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Horses and cows and chickens, everything was in the-- in the middle of the street and everybody was running.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who were those people?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the-- the inhabitants.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews, Poles, everybody was running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans I don't think were running away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they knew what was happening so they didn't run away but the Poles and the Jews were all running away.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
